The paper describes a system for predicting traffic flow, which involves processing spatio-temporal data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of biases to improve the performance of the model suggests that the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The use of temporal regression and attempts to incorporate spatial correlations suggest that the paper may also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) or systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
